{"metadata":{"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"text":"setTags:completion:","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setTags:completion:"}],"title":"setTags:completion:","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setTags:completion:"},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setTags:completion:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets user tags with a completion handler for confirmation."}],"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setTags:"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSDictionary","text":"NSDictionary","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"tags","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"completion:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void"},{"kind":"text","text":" (^"},{"kind":"text","text":")("},{"text":"NSError","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSError"},{"kind":"text","text":" * "},{"text":"error","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":")) ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"completion"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Dictionary of tag names and values to set for the current device."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Supported value types: NSString, NSNumber, NSArray (for list tags), NSNull (to delete).","type":"text"}]}],"name":"tags"},{"name":"completion","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Block called when the operation completes."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Receives nil on success, or an NSError describing the failure.","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Similar to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"setTags:"},{"text":" but provides feedback when the operation completes.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Use this when you need to:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Confirm tags were successfully set before proceeding"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Implement retry logic on failure"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Update UI based on tag update status"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Chain multiple operations that depend on tag updates"}]}]}]},{"level":2,"text":"Example","type":"heading","anchor":"Example"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Update subscription status with confirmation and retry:","type":"text"}]},{"code":["class SubscriptionManager {","","    private let maxRetries = 3","","    func updateSubscriptionStatus(_ subscription: Subscription,","                                  completion: @escaping (Result<Void, Error>) -> Void) {","        updateWithRetry(subscription: subscription, attempt: 1, completion: completion)","    }","","    private func updateWithRetry(subscription: Subscription, attempt: Int,","                                 completion: @escaping (Result<Void, Error>) -> Void) {","","        let tags: [String: Any] = [","            \"subscription_tier\": subscription.tier.rawValue,","            \"subscription_status\": subscription.isActive ? \"active\" : \"expired\",","            \"subscription_expiry\": ISO8601DateFormatter().string(from: subscription.expiryDate),","            \"is_premium\": subscription.tier != .free,","            \"features_enabled\": subscription.enabledFeatures.map { $0.rawValue }","        ]","","        Pushwoosh.configure.setTags(tags) { [weak self] error in","            if let error = error {","                if attempt < (self?.maxRetries ?? 3) {","                    let delay = Double(attempt) * 2.0","                    DispatchQueue.main.asyncAfter(deadline: .now() + delay) {","                        self?.updateWithRetry(subscription: subscription,","                                             attempt: attempt + 1,","                                             completion: completion)","                    }","                } else {","                    completion(.failure(error))","                }","                return","            }","","            Analytics.track(\"subscription_tags_updated\", properties: [","                \"tier\": subscription.tier.rawValue","            ])","            completion(.success(()))","        }","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"}],"kind":"content"}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/settags:completion:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","title":"PWConfiguration","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","kind":"symbol","abstract":[],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"PWConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/setTags:completion:":{"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setTags:completion:"}],"title":"setTags:completion:","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/settags:completion:","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setTags:completion:","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets user tags with a completion handler for confirmation."}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setTags:completion:","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"title":"PushwooshCore","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","role":"collection","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}]}}}